title: [Erica_Goodstone]Sexual Reawakening - 10 Simple Steps(EPUB+MOBI)
description:
Book Description
Publication Date: April 21, 2012
We are all sexual beings. When we our sensuality and sexual expression is awakened, we feel more fully alive. And by allowing full sexual expression into our life we cannot help but tune int, and become one with, our spiritual nature. Sexuality teaches. Sexuality heals. And sometimes our sexuality hurts. In this book you have a rare opportunity to explore the nuances of your own unique sexual love map and your persistent and lifelong sexual patterns as well as your needs, desires, preferences and beliefs about sexuality. Sexual expression happens naturally unless blocked in some way. Are you ready to face yourself, create passionate love relationships and allow more sensual and sexual pleasure into your life so that you can truly live in a greater state of love?
